@node 726 "726patch"

  Hi! After I Have relased muReset on Aminet, Adam Olivier
  send me a great idea how to improve muReset! Well it will
  be no muReset, but a shutdown deamon for Amiga. Now, Im at
  early stage of developing, but I have compiled a simple
  patch (726patch) that disallow to reset Your Amiga.

  Just try it, and write my back. Also, send some ideas to
  Adam Olivier <o.adam@francetelecom.com> .

  If it's fail to secure Your Amiga, send my a reset command You
  have used :-)

  And keep on waitin' for our shutdown deamon ;-)

@endnode

